":"2019-10-06T09:43:53.000Z","msg":"減黑警暴力?"},{"pid":"df64b5f92fb9599b96f36e26134a65086ba578fb","tid":1629543,"uid":94824,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"08c10b2953a13195d65a82931741a20fe6399704","tid":1629543,"uid":33099,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c4420614ced05eea9cfa27bbdac4fa5376b6ab44","tid":1629543,"uid":58863,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:39:40.000Z","msg":"余若海出黎食撚哂今日D TG佢啦<br />\n屌你老母仆街死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:41:25.000Z","msg":"我擔心呢條撚屌遲早俾人私了<br />\n<br />\n政府所有侵犯人權既case 都係佢經手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"係都報係余若薇度"},{"pid":"1c744321a18ed2c768acd04c18adcb540fb8a644","tid":1629543,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48ed4c0bc5fdb424a6ec59cb4a07284ceba9a05","tid":1629543,"uid":119012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"用結果去証明犯法可以無罪？<br />\n如果我殺左林病成個班子，全民即收手，係咪可以無罪？"},{"pid":"bd5cfc6a48a77df417633612e4922458d8516280","tid":1629543,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:00:41.000Z","msg":"多謝休息撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37adec912eb511b1c0b5b35d70755da110e046ad","tid":1629543,"uid":243162,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bd5cfc6a48a77df417633612e4922458d8516280","tid":1629543,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:00:41.000Z","msg":"多謝休息撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"你唔諗下佢本身個論點有問題之後你怪人休息？<br />\n用催淚彈黎衡量暴力？枝炮係人地到  人地用唔用係佢選擇  可唔可以咪再分化？<br />\n人地對家做到錯哂都唔割蓆  你自己割自己友蓆？"},{"pid":"fb0f8ef513fcbed686c323f43fd17ed59e5e2dc5","tid":1629543,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10: